      <li parentName="ul">{`The default along with its statements block is an optional one. The break statement can be placed at the end of default statements block.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`The default statements block can be placed at anywhere in the switch statement. If they are placed at any other place other than at end, it is compulsory to include a break statement at the end of default statements block.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Next-statement is a valid C statement.`}</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "important-rules-for-switch-statement"
